race.description: Bullseye Birdies Now In Town Handicap (C2)
race.comment: BATTLE ON BATTLER (3) came off the dirt and won a CL2 easily here and then made considerable ground in the run home placing close up this grade over 1403m. Peaks and keeps the handy 3kg claim. Draws a touch awkwardly but the step up to the mile looks ideal. NAVY SUN (4) resumed in the same race finishing just behind the above. Two back he led beaten 0.8L here over this distance and will go close with average luck in the run. BELVEDERE ROCK (5) was freshened off a first-up placing at Carnarvon and spaced the Maidens here by 2.3L. This is harder but he's heading in the right direction. MOONIEMIA (10) made sharp improvement just missing in the BATTLE ON BATTLER race starting at big odds. He raced forward and would be a hope if he can hold that form.
